<br>
I often use my epic to farm CC for velium I need for tradeskills.  While running around killing everything in sight, the epic pet keeps up pretty well even though I have Runspeed-3.<br>
<br>
Well I went down there recently and found I had camped with an Un-charged epic (doh!), and the spell wasn't memmed.  So not about to wait 5 minute, I get the 61 Air pet going instead.  <br>
<br>
Now it could be my imagination, but I really think the Air per was falling behind much more often than epic ever did.  I finally put my silverflank belt on and kept clicking it every time I moved a long distance.<br>
<br>
